{"tid":381053,"cid":13,"subCid":0,"title":"對皮boot發左霉點算","createTime":"2017-08-30T15:17:37.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-02T18:57:23.000Z","uid":75042,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"373208fed0cead67c316f3e00357e54907c57603","tid":381053,"uid":75042,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T15:17:37.000Z","msg":"夏天熱辣辣將對red wing pat左埋一邊<br />\n今日執野執出黎發現有一點點霉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n點樣可以清到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3990aed999be256629991d53aac27371cf9a09ce","tid":381053,"uid":117032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T15:19:56.000Z","msg":"松露<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ec7997a1253111c285a96c7daeef2aad2b8cd4a","tid":381053,"uid":75042,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T15:22:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>松露<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n又唔食得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我唔想對鞋有松露啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8f2595980f1aabd22c0a73bb010548e3364cea6","tid":381053,"uid":75042,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T15:22:19.000Z","msg":"Push<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"483743aad7266bec130e4fb36953b033d125aaec","tid":381053,"uid":75042,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T15:26:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a3df169a4e2cef143cbeebb3cfba7d25de48f7cf","tid":381053,"uid":123713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T15:34:38.000Z","msg":"有幾嚴重？<br />\n岩岩起個d 拎濕毛巾擦得走<br />\n霉左好耐 入晒入面 就冇得救啦"},{"pid":"7491072ebae1f8a8a7d52cefc160cbbaf9e22e39","tid":381053,"uid":75042,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T16:31:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有幾嚴重？<br />\n岩岩起個d 拎濕毛巾擦得走<br />\n霉左好耐 入晒入面 就冇得救啦</blockquote><br />\n係有啲一點點係對boot到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我google話用酒精抹得有冇巴打試過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76f880d3e464dd7925b1e6bf4482276bf94f5e8a","tid":381053,"uid":123713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T17:23:38.000Z","msg":"係入面應該救唔到喎<br />\n我就冇試過 <br />\n你可以係d唔顯眼既角落試少少睇下影唔影響塊皮既"},{"pid":"de837ea9869352bfa76191173f64d0bc1b4ec5ae","tid":381053,"uid":75042,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T02:54:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>係入面應該救唔到喎<br />\n我就冇試過 <br />\n你可以係d唔顯眼既角落試少少睇下影唔影響塊皮既</blockquote><br />\n今晚試下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我都打定輸數<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d26b36817fd386845f254039abb7c193565ce8f","tid":381053,"uid":127054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T02:57:07.000Z","msg":"威猛先生"},{"pid":"951a31773164156bc59ff12528410324d55c62ba","tid":381053,"uid":75042,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T02:57:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>威猛先生</blockquote><br />\n唔係洗廁所架咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a411c468defcb1984c789dfd4efd3ab7897d2386","tid":381053,"uid":98273,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T03:02:34.000Z","msg":"我之前對redwing比我阿媽擺係廁所<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n幾個月後想著番 一拎出黎成對都白撚哂 係佈滿霉菌<br />\n之後我抹走佢 變成咁<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/31/110223_b3781656441ad752324b2dae2767e307.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F31%2F110223_b3781656441ad752324b2dae2767e307.jpg&h=db72e619&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n然後扔撚左"},{"pid":"a05b67c92eba8cd454ea26814ab2146df7f8f258","tid":381053,"uid":75042,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T03:48:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我之前對redwing比我阿媽擺係廁所<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n幾個月後想著番 一拎出黎成對都白撚哂 係佈滿霉菌<br />\n之後我抹走佢 變成咁<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/31/110223_b3781656441ad752324b2dae2767e307.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F31%2F110223_b3781656441ad752324b2dae2767e307.jpg&h=db72e619&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n然後扔撚左</blockquote><br />\n巴打你個廁所好大架攞黎擺鞋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ？<br />\n我就係好似你張圖咁有一點點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔捨得掉啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"78cd377221dc9f9bc8b085f9a27d3971f0ba33c2","tid":381053,"uid":2340,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T04:28:15.000Z","msg":"我對9111 d皮龜裂左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da7af49e86fc0a41ef79c11c8826496194147007","tid":381053,"uid":75823,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T16:21:32.000Z","msg":"好彩我對RW剩係鞋頭車線發左霉,睇番應該係腳多踢垃圾時唔為意揩到D汁發霉"},{"pid":"963329618dcc305ee324ce2edf20c990182e50fa","tid":381053,"uid":18977,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T16:24:29.000Z","msg":"話平唔平 話貴唔貴 鄧你慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b94ed0598a356a626e75ac346be72